codes.code: argmax 'Given a list of Latin sentences with words that have missing endings marked with the character ~, predict the missing endings based on the context. Provide the answer only. Quī ab amīcīs proficīsc~ laet~ nōn potest. Choose from this set of possible answers [ entur iuntur, untur, itur, itur ētur untur itur, ī ārī, itur ārī] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'entur iuntur', 'untur', 'itur', 'itur ētur untur itur', 'ī ārī', 'itur ārī']
